title: Talkback/Text-to-Speech has very low distorted voice (compared to Google Assistant) on Pixel 3a
content:
Voice feedback will sometimes come out in an extremely low and distorted voice, borderline demonic effect, for lack of a better description.

Google Assistant usually sounds fine, but sometimes will use this voice. If I use Talkback or Text-to-speech, it will always use this distorted voice.

I am in Australia so language settings is set to English AU.
category: Google Assistant and Voice Actions, Google Pixel 3a
